---
import BaseLayout from "../layouts/BaseLayout.astro";

import ContactCTA from "../components/ContactCTA.astro";
import Hero from "../components/Hero.astro";
---

<BaseLayout title="About | Mathi Fonseca" description="About Mathi Fonseca">
    <div class="stack gap-20">
        <main class="wrapper about">
            <Hero
                title="About"
                tagline="Thanks for stopping by. Read below to learn more about myself and my background."
            >
                <img
                    width="1553"
                    height="873"
                    src="/assets/at-work.jpg"
                    alt="Mathi Fonseca at work with a colleague"
                />
            </Hero>

            <section>
                <div class="content bio">
                    <p>
                        I’m Mathi, a Principal Solutions Architect specialising
                        in payments, based in Berlin.
                    </p>
                    <p>
                        I’ve spent my career building and scaling payment
                        systems for some of Latin America and Europe’s largest
                        platforms — from the ground up and from multiple
                        different roles, becoming the living example of "if you
                        can't beat them, join them".
                    </p>
                    <p>
                        I’m equally comfortable defining a system's
                        architecture, integrating a PSP, or conducting a sales
                        demo. I’ve led cross-functional organisations, taught
                        Software Architecture at university level for 7 years,
                        and spoken at payments conferences across Europe.
                    </p>
                    <p>
                        Outside of payments: stoicism, teaching, beer, and being
                        the only Uruguayan that doesn't play football.
                    </p>
                </div>
            </section>
            <section>
                <h2 class="section-title">Building & Leadership</h2>
                <div class="content">
                    <p>
                        Over 15 years, I've built and scaled companies from the
                        ground up. As a founding team member at PedidosYa, I
                        helped grow it into a $2.5B GMV platform spanning 15
                        countries. At Payrails, I was the first employee —
                        growing the company to 100+ people across 9 teams.
                        Although I started my career as a headphones-always-on
                        coder, the startup fast-paced mindset taught me that
                        understanding the broader business and product context
                        was essential. Over time, I took on responsibilities
                        beyond pure technical work, including aligning with
                        business interests, collaborating with product and data
                        teams, and even working with sales teams. This holistic
                        approach has allowed me to better understand user needs,
                        prioritize development efforts, and drive value across
                        both technical and business dimensions.
                    </p>
                </div>
            </section>
            <section>
                <h2 class="section-title">Payments & Fraud</h2>
                <div class="content">
                    <p>
                        My expertise in payments and fraud prevention started as
                        just a project at PedidosYa, but ended up becoming my
                        main expertise. I led payments and fraud engineering
                        across the $2.5B GMV platform spanning 15 countries —
                        one of the highest-fraud payment environments in the
                        world — integrating 40+ PSP providers across Latam to
                        provide our users with the best payment experience while
                        keeping fraudsters out. After successfully building the
                        solution and leading the teams, I moved to Delivery Hero
                        HQ in Berlin. There I joined the Global Fintech team
                        when it was 3 people and helped grow it to 100+ people
                        across 8 specialised squads, overseeing payment
                        infrastructure for 50+ countries and $40B in annual GMV.
                        In my role as a Solutions Architect at Payrails, I
                        designed the product from the ground up, applying all
                        the lessons learned in the past to help global
                        businesses scale their payments and financial services.
                    </p>
                </div>
            </section>
            <section>
                <h2 class="section-title">Architecture & Engineering</h2>
                <div class="content">
                    <p>
                        My career spans a wide range of technical roles, with a
                        focus on software architecture and engineering
                        leadership. I’ve built and maintained complex systems,
                        worked with cutting-edge technologies, and designed
                        scalable and efficient platforms. This has included
                        collaborating with various engineering teams to ensure
                        alignment across diverse projects and global markets,
                        while maintaining consistency and high performance.
                        While my career steps led me to be further away from the
                        code and closer to the people, I never actually stopped
                        coding, it’s still one of the most fun parts of my job.
                    </p>
                </div>
            </section>
            <section>
                <h2 class="section-title">Teaching & Mentorship</h2>
                <div class="content">
                    <p>
                        Teaching has always been a driving force in my career.
                        For 7 years, I served as a Software Architecture and
                        Software Engineering in the Cloud professor at
                        Universidad ORT Uruguay, where I had the privilege and
                        challenge of sharing my knowledge with the next
                        generation of engineers. I've also spoken at payments
                        conferences across Europe. This passion for teaching
                        continues in my professional life, where I conduct
                        workshops, mentor colleagues, and foster growth and
                        knowledge-sharing within my teams. I am committed to
                        creating a culture of continuous learning and helping
                        others develop their skills.
                    </p>
                </div>
            </section>
            <section>
                <h2 class="section-title">Education</h2>
                <div class="content">
                    <p>
                        I hold a Bachelor of Science in Information Technology
                        and an advanced specialization in Big Data and Machine
                        Learning from Universidad ORT Uruguay. This academic
                        foundation supports my technical and leadership roles,
                        allowing me to stay at the forefront of industry trends
                        and continuously innovate in the fast-evolving fields of
                        technology and fintech.
                    </p>
                </div>
            </section>
        </main>

        <ContactCTA />
    </div>
</BaseLayout>

<style>
    .about {
        display: flex;
        flex-direction: column;
        gap: 3.5rem;
    }

    img {
        margin-top: 1.5rem;
        border-radius: 1.5rem;
        box-shadow: var(--shadow-md);
    }

    section {
        display: flex;
        flex-direction: column;
        gap: 0.5rem;
        color: var(--gray-200);
    }

    .section-title {
        grid-column-start: 1;
        font-size: var(--text-xl);
        color: var(--gray-0);
    }

    .content {
        grid-column: 2 / 4;
    }

    .bio p {
        margin-bottom: 1rem;
        line-height: 1.7;
        font-size: var(--text-lg);
    }

    .content :global(a) {
        text-decoration: 1px solid underline transparent;
        text-underline-offset: 0.25em;
        transition: text-decoration-color var(--theme-transition);
    }

    .content :global(a:hover),
    .content :global(a:focus) {
        text-decoration-color: currentColor;
    }

    @media (min-width: 50em) {
        .about {
            display: grid;
            grid-template-columns: 1fr 60% 1fr;
        }

        .about > :global(:first-child) {
            grid-column-start: 2;
        }

        section {
            display: contents;
            font-size: var(--text-lg);
        }
    }
</style>
